{"title":"想说一句话","authors":["杨远宏"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"想说一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨远宏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想说一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至对着摇晃的影子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至对着无言的栏杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想说一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河的波纹荡着霞光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的那句话　其实只像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边刚刚抽吐的嫩芽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿小船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像鱼尾一样摆动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿每一声婴儿的啼哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都像撒向河中的渔网"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实就是那朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开在船舱的灯花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在岸上等了很久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次次走回岸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河滩的卵石被踩得发白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处的家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉白的墙壁白了又黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐出嫁那天妈妈生下了我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我长成水田中碧绿的稻秧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实就像田边土坎的侧耳根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一样的平常而血红清亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又过了十年我开始写诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那句话我始终没有说出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它一定像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开门关门的声音那样动人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定会使钢铁开满带泪的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定像屋顶的炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那样优美动人"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}